42, 344.869], "heading level": 2, "font": "Verdana-Bold", "font size": 11.04, "text color": "[0.0]", "content": "32B. Terms and conditions for reduction or waiver of damages"}, {"type": "paragraph", "id": 642, "page number": 44, "bounding box": [88.704, 278.652, 549.37, 318.469], "font": "Verdana", "font size": 11.04, "text color": "[0.0]", "content": "The Central Board may reduce or waive the damages levied under section 14B of the Act in relation to an establishment specified in the second proviso to section 14B, subject to the following terms and conditions, namely: —"}, {"type": "list", "id": 643, "level": "9", "page number": 44, "bounding box": [88.704, 120.822, 549.361, 266.029], "numbering style": "english letters", "number of list items": 3, "list items": [{"type": "list item", "page number": 44, "bounding box": [88.704, 213.012, 549.088, 266.029], "font": "Verdana", "font size": 11.04, "text color": "[0.0]", "content": "(a) in case of a change of management including transfer of the undertaking to workers' co-operative and in case of merger or amalgamation of the sick industrial company with any other industrial company, complete waiver of damages may be allowed;", "kids": []}, {"type": "list item", "page number": 44, "bounding box": [88.704, 160.422, 549.101, 200.239], "font": "Verdana", "font size": 11.04, "text color": "[0.0]", "content": "(b) in cases where the Board for Industrial and Financial Reconstruction, for reasons to be recorded in its schemes, in this behalf recommends, waiver of damages up to 100 per cent may be allowed;", "kids": []}, {"type": "list item", "page number": 44, "bounding box": [88.704, 120.822, 549.361, 147.559], "font": "Verdana", "font size": 11.04, "text color": "[0.0]", "content": "(c) in other cases, depending on merits, reduction of damages up to 50 per cent may be allowed.", "kids": []}]}, {"type": "footer", "id": 644, "page number": 44, "bounding box": [265.85, 24.654, 539.704, 33.096], "kids": [{"type": "heading", "id"